âHi, master,â shouted the owner, disturbed at his meal, âthat be moine.â

âNot it, man,â yelled Hastings; âitâs mine; jump in,â and, without a
murmur, the worthy man obeyed.

âWhere to, master?â was the next inquiry.  âI be going for a load of
gravel to Scotland Yard.â  And within half an hour four bucks with white
