impossible in the Church, and so posterity was the loser of much pulpit
oratory that would doubtless have thrilled the present generation.

As we entered the âKitchenâ Jack Coneyâa promoted scene-shifter lately
come into prominence by his marriage with Rose Burtonâwas retailing to
