added: âRemove him, Colonel Crusoe.â  âColonel, sir?â inquired he.  âYes,
sir,â said I, âyouâre colonel from this very moment.ââ

The Colonel once expressed a desire to attend the Governorâs levÃ©e; but
bewailing the fact that he had not brought his uniform, he proceeded to
